<body>
  <main>
    <header>
      <h1>Security Policy</h1>
      <p class="sub">Last updated: 2025-08-22 • Applies to XRBitcoinCash (XRBC) websites, docs, and public code.</p>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2>Our commitment</h2>
      <p>We value the security of the XRBitcoinCash ecosystem and welcome responsible disclosures from the community. If you believe you’ve found a vulnerability, please report it to us so we can address it quickly and transparently.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>How to report</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Primary contact:</strong> <a href="mailto:security@xrbitcoincash.com">security@xrbitcoincash.com</a></li>
        <li><strong>Alternate contact:</strong> <a href="mailto:xrbitcoincash@gmail.com">xrbitcoincash@gmail.com</a></li>
        <li><strong>PGP/Encryption:</strong> <a href="https://xrbitcoincash.com/pgp-key.txt" class="mono">https://xrbitcoincash.com/pgp-key.txt</a></li>
        <li><strong>Security.txt:</strong> <a href="https://xrbitcoincash.com/.well-known/security.txt" class="mono">/.well-known/security.txt</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p class="small">Please include a clear description, affected URLs or components, steps to reproduce (PoC), impact assessment, and any logs or screenshots that help us verify the issue.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Scope</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>In scope:</strong> <span class="mono">xrbitcoincash.com</span> website and subpages, public repositories under the <span class="mono">XRBitcoinCash</span> GitHub organization, and XRBC-related configuration/metadata files (e.g., <span class="mono">/.well-known/xrp-ledger.toml</span>, <span class="mono">/.well-known/security.txt</span>).</li>
        <li><strong>Out of scope:</strong> Third‑party wallets, exchanges, or services not operated by XRBitcoinCash; issues requiring physical access; social engineering of our team or vendors.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Testing guidelines</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Allowed:</strong> Non‑destructive testing, read‑only research, and use of test accounts you control.</li>
        <li><strong>Do not:</strong> Exfiltrate data, modify or destroy content, impact availability (e.g., DoS/DDoS), send spam/phishing, or access accounts without permission.</li>
        <li><strong>Privacy first:</strong> If you encounter personal or sensitive data, stop and report immediately without copying or sharing it.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Coordinated disclosure & timelines</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Acknowledgement:</strong> We aim to acknowledge your report within 72 hours.</li>
        <li><strong>Initial assessment:</strong> Target triage within 7 business days.</li>
        <li><strong>Remediation:</strong> Timelines vary by severity; we strive to resolve critical issues as quickly as possible. We appreciate a standard 90‑day disclosure window.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Safe harbor</h2>
      <p>We will not pursue legal action against researchers who act in good faith, follow this policy, avoid privacy violations and service disruption, and give us a reasonable opportunity to remediate before public disclosure.</p>
      <p class="small">This safe harbor applies to research conducted under this policy and does not cover actions that are unlawful or out of scope.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Recognition & rewards</h2>
      <p>We maintain a public acknowledgements section for high‑impact reports. Monetary bounties are not guaranteed but may be awarded at our discretion based on severity, novelty, and quality of the report.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Versioning & contact</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Policy URL:</strong> <a href="https://xrbitcoincash.com/security-policy.html">https://xrbitcoincash.com/security-policy.html</a></li>
        <li><strong>Security.txt:</strong> <a href="https://xrbitcoincash.com/.well-known/security.txt">https://xrbitcoincash.com/.well-known/security.txt</a></li>
        <li><strong>PGP key:</strong> <a href="https://xrbitcoincash.com/pgp-key.txt">https://xrbitcoincash.com/pgp-key.txt</a></li>
        <li><strong>Contact:</strong> <a href="mailto:security@xrbitcoincash.com">security@xrbitcoincash.com</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <footer>
      <p>XRBitcoinCash • Security Policy • © 2025</p>
    </footer>
